{
  "stem": "6989.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really think it was standing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Immediate and the uncle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That uncle Motl that lived in back of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't remember it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, by the time they hid in the bunker for good, I wasn't there anymore, which I'll tell you about later.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I told you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like a door that sort of opened up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It looked like a closet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then you had to crawl into there, and then it suddenly opened up into a room, maybe 8 by 8.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, when I say a closet, it's funny, because their closets are like free standing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was what--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Linen.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yea.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know, linen probably.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because that's how I know how it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because then I never went in there again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just a couple of minutes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It had to be fast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Silent.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolute silence.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was very little.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No other little children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think we were just quiet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, frankly, you know, as I said to you, you see, I wasn't there when the full-- when they liquidated the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's when they really went into hiding.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because for the [NON-ENGLISH], you only went in for an hour or so until they were finished.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When you felt that the Germans left, you came out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once, I remember, only once.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just our family.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The father, mother, sisters, and the-- I think the uncle and one of the daughters was there too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember her going in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, she didn't want to go in, which I'll tell you about later.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
